# License Information

This repository contains multiple types of content with different licenses:


## 1. Berean Literal Bible (BLB) Text - Free Licensing

The **Berean Literal Bible** text (in `example/blb.csv` and column 18 of the
output TSV) is Copyright © 2015, 2022 by Bible Hub. It is made available under
free licensing for use in websites, apps, software, and audio.

For full terms: http://berean.bible/licensing.htm

Contact: bereanstudybible@aol.com


## 2. BSB / MSB Source Tables - Public Domain

The **Berean Standard Bible** and **Majority Standard Bible** interlinear source
tables (used as scaffold and training data) are dedicated to the **Public Domain**.

- Berean Standard Bible: https://bereanbible.com
- Majority Standard Bible: https://majoritybible.com

No attribution is required (though appreciated).


## 3. STEPBible Data - CC BY 4.0

The following data is created by **STEPBible.org** based on work at
**Tyndale House, Cambridge** and is licensed under
[Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/).

### TAGNT (Translators Amalgamated Greek New Testament)
- Files: `sources/tagnt_mat_jhn.txt`, `sources/tagnt_act_rev.txt`
- Source: https://github.com/STEPBible/STEPBible-Data
- Contains: Greek NT words with Strong's numbers, morphology, glosses, and
  text tradition data from all major editions (NA27/28, TR, Byz, SBL, WH, Treg, Tyn)

### Extended Strong's Lexicons
- Files: `sources/stepbible-tbesg.json` (Greek), `sources/stepbible-tbesh.json` (Hebrew)
- Source: https://github.com/STEPBible/STEPBible-Data
- Packaged by: https://www.npmjs.com/package/@metaxia/scriptures-source-stepbible-lexicon
- Contains: Glosses and definitions for all Strong's numbers

### Required Attribution (CC BY 4.0)

When using output data that incorporates STEPBible content, please include:

> Greek text data from TAGNT — Translators Amalgamated Greek New Testament
> ([STEPBible.org](https://www.STEPBible.org), CC BY 4.0).
> Data created by www.STEPBible.org based on work at Tyndale House, Cambridge.

For more details on the licence:
- You may include any part of this data in software or publications
  without requesting permission
- You may download and reformat the data for your application
- Proposed corrections should be sent to STEPBibleATgmail.com
- Please refer others to github.com/STEPBible as the source of the data


